{"type": "article", "id": 12503, "title": "“Light-Light 5”立灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-23T07:53:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153149xuvhGpSoMRKAVk3Q.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款极简主义的立灯，它的名字 “Light-Light 5” 来自构成灯的五个部分；大理石底座，灯绳，皮革搭扣，不锈钢支架和黄铜接口。组装起来非常简单可行，拧上灯泡便可以使用，而灯座和架子黑白两色对比，灯绳的轻巧和大理石的重量对比，彰显着设计细节上的用心。这是<a href=\"http://www.gaspardgraulich.com/V7/fr\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140228udKXgWDPmIlihN5j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41442543\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140228TmlOcnxp5FgJ1W47.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140228qm8Qr51jz7JREkBS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261402292poS3MUYv6OD5NlF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140230yQl2ognzSvRmaqu0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140230z0OorJQfyj58qaLU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140230TIQSedoc4A0CMPz6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140231UMiwEsDN7C8eWtvr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}